OL,3,CSteelworkers vote for strike action
OL,4,Cover Tata job losses
OL,6,FMembers of the largest steelworkers'
OL,7,Funion, Community, have voted in favour
OL,8,Fof industrial action over Tata Steel's
OL,9,Fplanned job cuts.
OL,11,FThe union said more than 85% of the
OL,12,F3,000 members surveyed voted for
OL,13,Findustrial action.
OL,15,FWorkers were balloted after Tata
OL,16,Fannounced 2,800 job losses across the
OL,17,FUK as part of the planned closure of
OL,18,FPort Talbot's blast furnaces,
OL,19,Fscheduled for the coming months, amid
OL,20,Fa transition to greener steelmaking.
