OL,6,FAlun Davies, national officer for
OL,7,Fsteel at Community, said: Alun Davies,
OL,8,FNational Officer for Steel at
OL,9,FCommunity, the steelworkers' union,
OL,10,Fsaid: "Today our members delivered
OL,11,Ftheir verdict on Tata Steel's job cuts
OL,12,Fplan, and they have voted to demand a
OL,13,Fbetter deal for the workforce.
OL,15,F"Community balloted more than 3,000
OL,16,Fmembers across all Tata Steel UK
OL,17,Fproduction sites, and more than 85%
OL,18,Fhave voted for industrial action.
