OL,4,Cover Tata job losses
OL,6,F"It should be noted this resounding
OL,7,Fmandate has been delivered in spite of
OL,8,Fthe company's bullying and
OL,9,Funacceptable threats to slash
OL,10,Fredundancy payments.
OL,12,F"We will now be consulting our members
OL,13,Fon next steps, and we urge Tata to
OL,14,Freconsider their position and get back
OL,15,Faround the table to head off a major
OL,16,Findustrial dispute.
