OL,6,F"It comes after Unite union announced
OL,7,Fin April that around 1,500 of its
OL,8,Fmembers based in Port Talbot and
OL,9,FLlanwern had "decisively" backed
OL,10,Findustrial action."
OL,12,FGMB union is yet to announce the
OL,13,Fresult of its ballot.
OL,15,FTata Steel plans to close both blast
OL,16,Ffurnaces in Port Talbot by the end of
OL,17,FSeptember. Tata say it is losing more
OL,18,Fthan #1million a day at the existing
OL,19,Foperation in south Wales.
